{% comment %} Template: page.shipping {% endcomment %}

<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Shipping Policy</h1>
  <p>Everything you need to know about shipping times, costs, and delivery options.</p>
</div>

<section class="policy-section">
  <div class="policy-container">
    <div class="policy-content">
      <h2>Processing Time</h2>
      <p>We process orders within 1-2 business days. Same-day shipping available for orders placed before 2:00 PM CST.</p>

      <h2>Shipping Rates</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Free Shipping:</strong> Orders over $50 (Continental US only)</li>
        <li><strong>Standard Shipping (3-7 days):</strong> $9.99</li>
        <li><strong>Express Shipping (2-3 days):</strong> $19.99</li>
        <li><strong>Next Day Shipping:</strong> Calculated at checkout</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Delivery Times</h2>
      <p>Standard shipping takes 3-7 business days depending on your location. Express shipping delivers within 2-3 business days. Delivery times are estimates and begin after your order has been processed and shipped.</p>

      <h2>In-Store Pickup</h2>
      <p>Available for local customers! Select "In-Store Pickup" at checkout. We'll email you when your order is ready (usually within 24 hours during business hours).</p>
      <p><strong>Pickup Location:</strong><br>113 South Center<br>Grand Prairie, TX 75050<br>Mon–Fri 9am–6pm, Sat 9am–12pm CST</p>

      <h2>International Shipping</h2>
      <p>Yes, we ship internationally! Contact us for shipping rates to your location. International orders may be subject to customs fees and import duties, which are the responsibility of the buyer.</p>

      <h2>Order Tracking</h2>
      <p>Tracking numbers are automatically sent to your email once your order ships. You can also track your order status by logging into your account.</p>

      <h2>Lost or Damaged Packages</h2>
      <p>If your package is lost or arrives damaged, please contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:viceliatinde20@gmail.com">viceliatinde20@gmail.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+12146771059">(214) 677-1059</a>. We'll work with the carrier to resolve the issue and get you a replacement or refund.</p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:viceliatinde20@gmail.com">viceliatinde20@gmail.com</a> or <a href="tel:+12146771059">(214) 677-1059</a> for any shipping questions.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.policy-section { padding: 3rem 0 5rem; }
.policy-container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
.policy-content h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem; color: var(--clutch-accent); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
.policy-content h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
.policy-content p { color: var(--clutch-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }
.policy-content ul { margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--clutch-text-muted); }
.policy-content li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.policy-content strong { color: var(--clutch-text); }
.policy-content a { color: var(--clutch-accent); text-decoration: none; }
.policy-content a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
